{"tid":746232,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚有冇人用133打錯電話？","createTime":"2018-07-17T11:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T17:07:01.000Z","uid":169028,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cdb41b77eca3a703ddfed5c3f92cc3b70800651b","tid":746232,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:45:38.000Z","msg":"話說<br />\n琴晚(17/7)凌晨1時40分，有個&rdquo;沒有來電顯示&rdquo;嘅電話打黎<br />\n聽左之後，係一把男仔聲，佢用一把講秘密嘅聲講野<br />\n電話短達一分鐘，我已經唔係好記得個內容係咩，但大約係佢係咁講同屋企人炒大獲，我就不停問佢係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢： 我岩岩同屋企人炒左大獲<br />\n我：下？你係邊個？<br />\n（我男朋友係我隔離，要我較擴音）<br />\n佢：睇下whatsapp<br />\n我：你係邊個？<br />\n佢：你估下<br />\n我：下，我唔知你係邊個<br />\n之後佢就cut左我線<br />\n我睇番whatsapp，又無人搵過我<br />\n<br />\n然後，我男朋友以為我出面有第二個嬲左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟邊個仆街陰9我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你打錯電話既話 可唔可以講番聲打錯阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93a52a88ad1c92c67678e4df49c4b6fac4fc841","tid":746232,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"無錯，我係陰你"},{"pid":"1f6945ea7cd11d3e4c166498263677e04d02d4ed","tid":746232,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e93a52a88ad1c92c67678e4df49c4b6fac4fc841","tid":746232,"uid":138138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:46:40.000Z","msg":"無錯，我係陰你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T11:48:06.000Z","msg":"我無得罪你 點解要陰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a617eb5ce934feb9f0217e427de66eb413b99a6a","tid":746232,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f6945ea7cd11d3e4c166498263677e04d02d4ed","tid":746232,"uid":169028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e93a52a88ad1c92c67678e4df49c4b6fac4fc841","tid":746232,"uid":138138,"